OL,3,CSwinney using Reform's 'race baiting'
OL,4,Cattack to score political points `
OL,5,CSarwar
OL,7,FScottish Labour's leader Anas Sarwar
OL,8,Fhas accused John Swinney of using
OL,9,FReform's "race baiting" attack to
OL,10,Fscore political points against him,
OL,11,Fsaying he finds it "harder to stomach".
OL,13,FLast year's Reform advert attacked Mr
OL,14,FSarwar, accusing him of seeking to
OL,15,Fprioritise Pakistani people.
OL,17,FThe ad quoted him calling for more
OL,18,Frepresentation for people from south
OL,19,FAsian communities.
OL,26,@qD@JOUqD@WO]sD@TOUsD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
