FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775369052
OL,3,CSwinney using Reform's 'race baiting'
OL,4,Cattack to score political points `
OL,5,CSarwar
OL,7,FMr Sarwar has accused the SNP of using
OL,8,FReform's message for their own
OL,9,Fpolitical gain by suggesting that
OL,10,FLabour would make a deal with the
OL,11,Fparty.
OL,13,FSpeaking to the Press Association on
OL,14,FFriday, Mr Sarwar said: "Do I think
OL,15,FReform will try and do race baiting in
OL,16,Fthis election campaign? Yes they will,
OL,17,Fbut I expect that from them. That is
OL,18,Fwho they are, and that's why Scotland,
OL,19,FI'm confident, will reject them.
OL,26,@vD@YOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775369052
OL,3,CSwinney using Reform's 'race baiting'
OL,4,Cattack to score political points `
OL,5,CSarwar
OL,7,F"What I find harder to stomach is why
OL,8,Fsomeone like John Swinney and the SNP
OL,9,Fwould use the race baiting of the
OL,10,FReform Party and use it as a way to
OL,11,Fattack me."
OL,13,FThomas Kerr, a senior figure in Reform
OL,14,Fand one of its Holyrood candidates,
OL,15,Fsaid he could not rule out re-airing
OL,16,Fthe ad from last year attacking Mr
OL,17,FSarwar.
OL,19,FThe advert was branded "racist" by
OL,20,FScottish Labour leader Mr Sarwar and
OL,21,FFirst Minister John Swinney.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@KO]{D@XOU{D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775369052
OL,3,CSwinney using Reform's 'race baiting'
OL,4,Cattack to score political points `
OL,5,CSarwar
OL,7,FHowever Mr Sarwar has now said that
OL,8,Fthe SNP leader had used the advert to
OL,9,Fmake a political point, attack him and
OL,10,Fclaim Labour would make a deal with
OL,11,FReform.
OL,13,FHe continued: "What was the SNP's
OL,14,Fresponse? It was to say, this is the
OL,15,Fpeople that Labour is going to do a
OL,16,Fdeal with, using the race baiting to
OL,17,Fattack me when I'm the person that
OL,18,FReform is trying to race bait.
OL,20,F"I think that's beneath John Swinney
OL,21,Fand I think that's beneath the SNP.
OL,26,@uD@OOU|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
