OL,3,CSwinney using Reform's 'race baiting'
OL,4,Cattack to score political points `
OL,5,CSarwar
OL,7,F"Let's have a debate on the ideas for
OL,8,Fthis country, let's have a debate on
OL,9,Fthe future of our NHS in this country,
OL,10,Fthe opportunities for our kids in this
OL,11,Fcountry, how we respect people's
OL,12,Fmoney, how we transform our
OL,13,Fcommunities, and how we make sure this
OL,14,Fgreat country, Scotland, meets the
OL,15,Fneeds and the aspirations of our
OL,16,Famazing people."
OL,18,FMalcolm Offord, Reform UK Scotland
OL,19,Fleader, unveiled two election campaign
OL,20,Fvans on Wednesday while in Glasgow's
OL,21,Feast end.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
