OL,3,CSwinney using Reform's 'race baiting'
OL,4,Cattack to score political points `
OL,5,CSarwar
OL,7,FThey showed migrants, all non-white,
OL,8,Fon a small boat along with the words
OL,9,F"Scotland is at breaking point" with a
OL,10,Fcaption below reading: "Glasgow has
OL,11,Fbecome the illegal migrant capital of
OL,12,Fthe UK. Only Reform Scotland will stop
OL,13,Fthis."
OL,15,FMr Sarwar continued: "I'm not
OL,16,Fsuggesting that the SNP and Reform
OL,17,Fhave the same politics, I'm not
OL,18,Fsuggesting they have the same values,
OL,19,FI'm not suggesting that they have the
OL,20,Fsame brand of politics.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@_O]rD@XOUuD@FO]wD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775369052
OL,3,CSwinney using Reform's 'race baiting'
OL,4,Cattack to score political points `
OL,5,CSarwar
OL,7,F"It would be wrong for me to suggest
OL,8,Fthat, but I think fundamentally, what
OL,9,Fmakes them similar, though, is that
OL,10,Fthey play the politics of fear and
OL,11,Fblame.
OL,13,F"And I think for far too long, we've
OL,14,Fhad politicians in this country that
OL,15,Frightly identify a problem that we
OL,16,Fface but rather than find a solution,
OL,17,Flook to find somebody to blame for it."
OL,19,FA spokesperson for the SNP said: "The
OL,20,Fbillboard was an utter disgrace and
OL,21,Fhas no place in Scottish politics.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUyD@gO]{D@bOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
