FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775369052
OL,3,CSwinney using Reform's 'race baiting'
OL,4,Cattack to score political points `
OL,5,CSarwar
OL,7,F"That is exactly why Anas Sarwar must
OL,8,Fconfirm he won't rely on the votes of
OL,9,FReform to force his way into Bute
OL,10,FHouse.
OL,12,F"Anas Sarwar's issue is not with the
OL,13,FSNP, his issue is with his own party
OL,14,Fwho have briefed out that the Scottish
OL,15,FLabour Party is plotting exactly that."
OL,17,FReform Scotland have been approached
OL,18,Ffor comment.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUwD@gO]
